<p id="_763c588f-f0a7-fba2-d2f3-8a0fd320728e">With this mean based on only two determinations, the CCL considered it prudent to assume an estimated relative standard uncertainty of <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mn>4</mn>
    <mo>×</mo>
    <msup>
      <mn>10</mn>
      <mrow>
        <mo>−</mo>
        <mn>10</mn>
      </mrow>
    </msup>
  </mstyle>
